OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Boiler tax' plan to boost 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fheat pump sales delayed    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government is delaying the         
OL,6, implementation of fines for boiler     
OL,7, manufacturers who do not hit heat pump 
OL,8, sales targets.                         
OL,10,FThe so-called "boiler tax" is designed 
OL,11,Fto encourage households away from      
OL,12,Ftraditional gas boilers and towards    
OL,13,Fgreener heating methods.               
OL,15,FCritics say delaying the tax from 1    
OL,16,FApril to next year will not help the UK
OL,17,Fmeet its emissions targets.            
OL,19,FBut the government said it will also   
OL,20,Fmake heat pump grants easier to get.   
